{"tid":1619114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭： 你地遍地開花","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:59:57.000Z","uid":223216,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"59037f3b73a3c72a30acb33809a0c9aca91bbe5c","tid":1619114,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:34.000Z","msg":"黑警唔夠人手啦<br />\n之前一兩區 我地咪夠打囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地搞到其他鋪<br />\n搞到中資，搞到福建幫，搞到紅色資本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地以前掟汽油彈掟死物<br />\n依家掟黨鐵 掟黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於威脅到佢地啦<br />\n<br />\n凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護，凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對！<br />\n革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動。"},{"pid":"a3ce0b4bfb51ac37fb9f960468919f799aab4403","tid":1619114,"uid":26721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明有效 勿集中一區"},{"pid":"f68f4a2cc8b6aa4f0526633994bfa10d1d092d38","tid":1619114,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"推翻政權！！！"},{"pid":"395cf6e9f746dea26f9e51a8b2be0d2ac4ebb7c3","tid":1619114,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵貴神速 今晚就要先聲奪人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"054cfd3590732038a921267cbc5afbf3e0b4da18","tid":1619114,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"推翻政權！！"},{"pid":"4ff6646de513728bb948382c96fced99f17fb976","tid":1619114,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f542b737f1bb1a219e8aa4039b90de3f077caeb","tid":1619114,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"遍地開花"},{"pid":"8dfb1b2e6e8a894f5b94618c7457907fe4393cbb","tid":1619114,"uid":46814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見，撳錢是真理"},{"pid":"e49374715015342cbf32def0d232cec10f8eea30","tid":1619114,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb4421e58110e79d1f4c6b67917a11a0aaa34ec","tid":1619114,"uid":196549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"繼續遍地開花！"},{"pid":"e19cd670261694ed33989839e4f7b00340c7bed6","tid":1619114,"uid":70859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"18區開花，唔好去政總<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1619215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1619215</a><br />\n<br />\n行政署向政府總部的員工發電郵，指政總員工可以在今日下午3時半後下班。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有政總員工表示，多名警察在午飯時間手持槍枝進入政總戒備。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=057855a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&h=9b6f7ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金鐘佢地已經打到熟晒<br />\n知道晒我地有咩不足、點樣可以捉到最多人<br />\n而家已經有晒部署駐晒兵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔好再打冇把握嘅仗，去返自己地頭，遍地開花！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dad749e5794417511e7dbfb882caf37c05cfdede","tid":1619114,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f83653d2cc62cf4b105808198e327d90a8990b","tid":1619114,"uid":40979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce72583292afa90a68d6e4a500f869729d9fd9b9","tid":1619114,"uid":266747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc1fbec8a9123956b4fc150d9214d723ed25501","tid":1619114,"uid":200328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"遍地開花唔夠<br />\n要遍地勇武<br />\n全民轉職"},{"pid":"8a0df83b13d775f42badd3536b3db638e33ee038","tid":1619114,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"講真丫, 照黎6區睇帶mask 照開波 你要拉當場都拉左, 比你拉到mask唔mask都冇分別啦吊。 聽日全港開花!"},{"pid":"9685d90f45d247389c5c08d0770cbd2a4b5025ba","tid":1619114,"uid":223216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dfb1b2e6e8a894f5b94618c7457907fe4393cbb","tid":1619114,"uid":46814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,